title: Extrawelt - Der Dicke Mann Von Nebenan
description:
Official Oliver Lieb Youtube Channel.

Written and produced by Arne Schaffhausen & Wayan Raabe in 2009
Remastered by Oliver Lieb 2013

Maschine  is proud to present release number 16!
Extrawelt - Error Medley EP
Not much need to introduce Extrawelt.
Arne and Wayan submitted three great pieces of music on this release.
 
Buy this lossless at Bandcamp:
http://oliverlieb.bandcamp.com/album/error-medley-ep
Buy this at Itunes :
https://itunes.apple.com/de/album/id674048667?affId=1108120
Buy this at Beatport:
http://www.beatport.com/release/error-medley-ep/1126803
Buy this at Junodownload:
http://www.junodownload.com/products/2251362-2.htm

Oliver Lieb at Bandcamp: http://oliverlieb.bandcamp.com 
Oliver Lieb at Beatport: https://www.beatport.com/artist/oliver-lieb/4180 
Solieb Digital at Beatport: https://www.beatport.com/label/solieb-digital/11760
Oliver Lieb on the web: 
Official Website: http://www.oliverlieb.com Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/oliverlieb 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/oliverliebmusic/
Twitter: http://twitter.com/#!/oliverlieb Soundcloud: http://www.soundcloud.com/oliver-lieb 
Solieb Digital Facebook page: http://www.facebook.com/soliebdigital 

Frankfurt based DJ & producer Oliver Lieb is involved in the production of electronic music since 1988. With more than 300 singles and albums including remixes for Faithless, Moby, Snap, Yello, Human League, Mory Kante, Utah Saints to name a few, he made it in the premier leage of international producers and keeps surprising and amazing people with his extraordinary sounds and diversity. 

This Channel has playlists for his labels Maschine for new releases & Solieb Digital where he releases re-mastered versions of his old classic productions as well as playlists for new releases on other labels and videos from events.
